#: templates/homepage.html:51
msgid "Designed for Global Scale"
msgstr "Iliyoundwa kwa Kiwango cha Kimataifa"

#: templates/homepage.html:52
msgid "Everything you need to manage complex global payroll operations with confidence"
msgstr "Kila kitu unachohitaji ili kusimamia shughuli tata za mishahara ya kimataifa kwa ujasiri"

#: templates/homepage.html:57
msgid "AI-Powered Compliance"
msgstr "Uzingatiaji Unaowezeshwa na AI"

#: templates/homepage.html:58
msgid "Automated regulatory updates and risk assessment across all jurisdictions with machine learning algorithms."
msgstr "Masasisho ya kanuni za kiotomatiki na tathmini ya hatari katika mamlaka zote kwa kutumia algoriti za ujifunzaji wa mashine."

#: templates/homepage.html:62
msgid "Real-time Analytics"
msgstr "Uchanganuzi wa Wakati Halisi"

#: templates/homepage.html:63
msgid "Comprehensive dashboards with live insights into payroll costs, compliance status, and operational metrics."
msgstr "Dashibodi kamili zenye maarifa ya moja kwa moja kuhusu gharama za mishahara, hali ya uzingatiaji, na vipimo vya uendeshaji."

#: templates/homepage.html:67
msgid "Instant Processing"
msgstr "Uchakataji wa Papo Hapo"

#: templates/homepage.html:68
msgid "Batch process thousands of payments across different currencies and banking systems simultaneously."
msgstr "Chakata kwa mfumo wa kundi maelfu ya malipo katika sarafu na mifumo ya benki tofauti kwa wakati mmoja."

#: templates/homepage.html:72
msgid "Enterprise Security"
msgstr "Usalama wa Kiwango cha Biashara"

#: templates/homepage.html:73
msgid "Bank-grade encryption, multi-factor authentication, and SOC 2 Type II certified infrastructure."
msgstr "Usimbaji wa kiwango cha benki, uthibitishaji wa hatua nyingi (MFA), na miundombinu iliyoidhinishwa SOC 2 Aina ya II."

#: templates/homepage.html:77
msgid "Global Coverage"
msgstr "Ufunikaji wa Kimataifa"

#: templates/homepage.html:78
msgid "Seamless payroll processing across 40+ countries with local compliance and tax expertise built-in."
msgstr "Uchakataji wa mishahara usio na vikwazo katika nchi zaidi ya 40 ukiwa na uzingatiaji wa ndani na utaalamu wa kodi uliojengewa ndani."

#: templates/homepage.html:82
msgid "Audit Trail"
msgstr "Rekodi ya Ukaguzi"

#: templates/homepage.html:83
msgid "Complete transparency with immutable records for every transaction and compliance verification."
msgstr "Uwazi kamili wenye rekodi zisizobadilika kwa kila muamala na uthibitishaji wa uzingatiaji."

#: templates/homepage.html:90
msgid "Unified Platform"
msgstr "Jukwaa Lililounganishwa"

#: templates/homepage.html:91
msgid "Everything in One Dashboard"
msgstr "Kila Kitu katika Dashibodi Moja"

#: templates/homepage.html:92
msgid "Manage your entire global payroll operation from a single, intuitive interface with real-time data and actionable insights."
msgstr "Simamia operesheni yako yote ya mishahara ya kimataifa kutoka kiolesura kimoja rahisi kueleweka chenye data ya wakati halisi na maarifa yanayotekelezeka."

#: templates/homepage.html:97
msgid "Monitor payroll costs, compliance status, and operational metrics across all regions with live dashboards."
msgstr "Fuatilia gharama za mishahara, hali ya uzingatiaji, na vipimo vya uendeshaji katika maeneo yote kwa dashibodi za moja kwa moja."

#: templates/homepage.html:101
msgid "Multi-currency Support"
msgstr "Msaada wa Sarafu Nyingi"

#: templates/homepage.html:102
msgid "Process payments in 40+ currencies with automated forex management and optimal exchange rates."
msgstr "Chakata malipo katika sarafu zaidi ya 40 kwa usimamizi wa forex wa kiotomatiki na viwango bora vya ubadilishaji."

#: templates/homepage.html:106
msgid "Automated Reporting"
msgstr "Ripoti za Kiotomatiki"

#: templates/homepage.html:107
msgid "Generate compliance reports, tax filings, and financial statements automatically across all jurisdictions."
msgstr "Tengeneza ripoti za uzingatiaji, taarifa za kodi, na taarifa za fedha kiotomatiki katika mamlaka zote."

