#: templates/homepage.html:138
msgid "Bank-Grade Protection"
msgstr "Ulinzi wa Kiwango cha Benki"

#: templates/homepage.html:139
msgid "Your global payroll data is protected by multiple layers of enterprise security"
msgstr "Data yako ya mishahara ya kimataifa inalindwa na tabaka nyingi za usalama wa kiwango cha biashara"

#: templates/homepage.html:143
msgid "AES-256 Encryption"
msgstr "Usimbaji AES-256"

#: templates/homepage.html:144
msgid "All data encrypted in transit and at rest with military-grade encryption standards."
msgstr "Data yote imesimbwa wakati wa usafirishaji na inapohifadhiwa kwa viwango vya usimbaji wa kiwango cha kijeshi."

#: templates/homepage.html:148
msgid "Multi-Factor Auth"
msgstr "Uthibitishaji wa Hatua Nyingi"

#: templates/homepage.html:149
msgid "Enterprise-grade MFA with biometric options for all user access levels."
msgstr "MFA ya kiwango cha biashara yenye chaguo za kibayometriki kwa viwango vyote vya ufikiaji wa watumiaji."

#: templates/homepage.html:153
msgid "SOC 2 Certified"
msgstr "Imeidhinishwa SOC 2"

#: templates/homepage.html:154
msgid "Regular third-party audits ensure continuous compliance with security standards."
msgstr "Ukaguzi wa mara kwa mara wa wahusika wengine huhakikisha uzingatiaji endelevu wa viwango vya usalama."

#: templates/homepage.html:158
msgid "Data Sovereignty"
msgstr "Ukuu wa Data"

#: templates/homepage.html:159
msgid "Regional data centers ensure compliance with local data protection regulations."
msgstr "Vituo vya data vya kikanda huhakikisha uzingatiaji wa kanuni za ulinzi wa data za ndani."

#: templates/homepage.html:165
