#: templates/homepage.html:167
msgid "See how companies are transforming their global payroll operations with ExactusPay"
msgstr "Ona jinsi makampuni yanavyobadilisha operesheni zao za mishahara ya kimataifa kwa ExactusPay"

#: templates/homepage.html:171
msgid ""
"\"ExactusPay revolutionized our global payroll operations. We reduced processing time by 80% while eliminating compliance errors across 15 countries. Their platform paid for itself within the first quarter, and the ROI has been phenomenal.\""
msgstr ""
"\"ExactusPay ilibadilisha kabisa operesheni zetu za mishahara ya kimataifa. Tulipunguza muda wa uchakataji kwa 80% huku tukiondoa makosa ya uzingatiaji katika nchi 15. Jukwaa lao lilijilipa ndani ya robo ya kwanza, na faida kwa uwekezaji (ROI) imekuwa ya ajabu.\""

